{{infobox theatre festival | theatre_festival_name = Smile of Sarajevo Theatre Festival | image = File:Smile.of.sarajevo.fest.jpg | caption = | location = [[Sarajevo]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]] | selector = [[Ermin Sijamija]] | founded = 2017 | founders = Nedžad Podžić | dates = May | playtype = | website = }} The '''Smile of Sarajevo Theatre Festival''' ({{lang-bs|Festival komedije Osmijeh Sarajeva / Фестивал комедије Осмијех Сарајева}}) is an international [[comedy]] [[theatre festival]] that is annually held in [[Sarajevo]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fokus.ba/vijesti/kultura/proglasenjem-pobjednika-zatvoren-festival-pozorisne-komedije-osmijeh-sarajeva/734594/|title=Zatvoren Festival pozorišne komedije "Osmijeh Sarajeva"|publisher=fokus.ba}}</ref> It was established in 2017 by a team of theatre professionals headed by Nedžad Podžić "Poćko". The festival is organized in May and lasts for 9 days.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://coolstyle.ba/uskoro-pocinje-festival-osmijeh-sarajeva-ceka-nas-devet-dana-smijeha-i-dobre-muzike/|title=Uskoro počinje Festival "Osmijeh Sarajeva": Čeka nas devet dana smijeha i dobre muzike|publisher=coolstyle.ba}}</ref> It showcases comedy theatre performances from Bosnia and Herzegovina and the [[Former Yugoslavia]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://depo.ba/clanak/160721/festival-komedije-osmijeh-sarajeva-od-12-do-20-maja-bogat-pozorisni-program-i-ludi-after-partyji|title=Festival komedije 'Osmijeh Sarajeva' od 12. do 20. maja: Bogat pozorišni program i ludi after partyji|publisher=depo.ba}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.klix.ba/magazin/kultura/festival-osmijeh-sarajeva-najboljom-predstavom-proglasena-izvedba-ime-teatra-komedija-iz-skoplja/170520087|title=Festival Osmijeh Sarajeva: Najboljom predstavom proglašena izvedba "Ime", Teatra Komedija iz Skoplja|publisher=klix.ba}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.klix.ba/magazin/kultura/osmijeh-sarajeva-oficijelni-program-prvog-festivala-komedije-u-bih/170418062|title=Osmijeh Sarajeva: Oficijelni program prvog festivala komedije u BiH|publisher=klix.ba}}</ref>
